<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT6">
<l>aṟiyār camaṇa rayarttār pavuttar</l>
<l>ciṟiyār civappaṭṭār ceppil veṟiyāya</l>
<l>māyavaṉai mālavaṉai mātavaṉai yēttātā</l>
<l>rīṉavarē yātalā liṉṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Jains do not know [the truth], the Buddhists have forgotten [it],</l>
<l>Śiva’s priests [are] insignificant people.</l>
<l>To tell [the truth], those [who] do not praise the fragrant Dark [Lord],</l>
<l rend="indent">Mālavaṉ, Mādhavaṉ</l>
<l>are therefore base people now.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
